txt.en: 'Dead or alive, you'll do just fine to get me running this place!'
'I am glad that my family and I are safe, thanks to you.'
'My family and I were kidnapped from Crithost.'
'I just want to play hide and seek with my friend, Tolwin, again.'
'This filth here is my bargaining chip for power in this place!'
'If they were going to eat us, you'd think they'd give us some food.'
'Well this didn't work out as I planned.'
'You want me to add you to my stock pile? Fine!'
